metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of runs cancelled for this workspace. Count is updated when a run is successfully cancelled.
metricSpecifications.name: Cancelled Runs

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of runs where cancel was requested for this workspace. Count is updated when cancellation request has been received for a run.
metricSpecifications.name: Cancel Requested Runs

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of runs completed successfully for this workspace. Count is updated when a run has completed and output has been collected.
metricSpecifications.name: Completed Runs

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of runs failed for this workspace. Count is updated when a run fails.
metricSpecifications.name: Failed Runs

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of runs entered finalizing state for this workspace. Count is updated when a run has completed but output collection still in progress.
metricSpecifications.name: Finalizing Runs

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of runs not responding for this workspace. Count is updated when a run enters Not Responding state.
metricSpecifications.name: Not Responding Runs

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of runs in Not Started state for this workspace. Count is updated when a request is received to create a run but run information has not yet been populated.
metricSpecifications.name: Not Started Runs

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of runs that are preparing for this workspace. Count is updated when a run enters Preparing state while the run environment is being prepared.
metricSpecifications.name: Preparing Runs

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of runs that are provisioning for this workspace. Count is updated when a run is waiting on compute target creation or provisioning.
metricSpecifications.name: Provisioning Runs

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of runs that are queued for this workspace. Count is updated when a run is queued in compute target. Can occure when waiting for required compute nodes to be ready.
metricSpecifications.name: Queued Runs

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of runs running for this workspace. Count is updated when run starts running on required resources.
metricSpecifications.name: Started Runs

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of runs started for this workspace. Count is updated after request to create run and run info, such as the Run Id, has been populated
metricSpecifications.name: Starting Runs

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of run errors in this workspace. Count is updated whenever run encounters an error.
metricSpecifications.name: Errors

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of run warnings in this workspace. Count is updated whenever a run encounters a warning.
metricSpecifications.name: Warnings

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Percentage of utilization on a CPU node. Utilization is reported at one minute intervals.

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Percentage of utilization on a GPU node. Utilization is reported at one minute intervals.

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Percentage of memory utilization on a GPU node. Utilization is reported at one minute intervals.
metricSpecifications.name: GpuMemoryUtilization

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Interval energy in Joules on a GPU node. Energy is reported at one minute intervals.
metricSpecifications.name: GpuEnergyJoules

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Utilization of a CPU node in millicores. Utilization is aggregated in one minute intervals.
metricSpecifications.name: CpuUtilizationMillicores

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Maximum capacity of a CPU node in millicores. Capacity is aggregated in one minute intervals.
metricSpecifications.name: CpuCapacityMillicores

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Utilization percentage of a CPU node. Utilization is aggregated in one minute intervals.
metricSpecifications.name: CpuUtilizationPercentage

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Utilization of a GPU device in milli-GPUs. Utilization is aggregated in one minute intervals.
metricSpecifications.name: GpuUtilizationMilliGPUs

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Utilization percentage of a GPU device. Utilization is aggregated in one minute intervals.
metricSpecifications.name: GpuUtilizationPercentage

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Maximum capacity of a GPU device in milli-GPUs. Capacity is aggregated in one minute intervals.
metricSpecifications.name: GpuCapacityMilliGPUs

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Memory utilization of a GPU device in megabytes. Utilization aggregated in at one minute intervals.
metricSpecifications.name: GpuMemoryUtilizationMegabytes

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Maximum memory capacity of a GPU device in megabytes. Capacity aggregated in at one minute intervals.
metricSpecifications.name: GpuMemoryCapacityMegabytes

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Memory utilization percentage of a GPU device. Utilization aggregated in at one minute intervals.
metricSpecifications.name: GpuMemoryUtilizationPercentage

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Memory utilization percentage of a CPU node. Utilization is aggregated in one minute intervals.
metricSpecifications.name: CpuMemoryUtilizationPercentage

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Memory utilization of a CPU node in megabytes. Utilization is aggregated in one minute intervals.
metricSpecifications.name: CpuMemoryUtilizationMegabytes

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Maximum memory utilization of a CPU node in megabytes. Utilization is aggregated in one minute intervals.
metricSpecifications.name: CpuMemoryCapacityMegabytes

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Network data received in megabytes. Metrics are aggregated in one minute intervals.
metricSpecifications.name: NetworkInputMegabytes

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Network data sent in megabytes. Metrics are aggregated in one minute intervals.
metricSpecifications.name: NetworkOutputMegabytes

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Network data received over InfiniBand in megabytes. Metrics are aggregated in one minute intervals.
metricSpecifications.name: IBReceiveMegabytes

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Network data sent over InfiniBand in megabytes. Metrics are aggregated in one minute intervals.
metricSpecifications.name: IBTransmitMegabytes

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Used disk space in megabytes. Metrics are aggregated in one minute intervals.
metricSpecifications.name: DiskUsedMegabytes

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Available disk space in megabytes. Metrics are aggregated in one minute intervals.
metricSpecifications.name: DiskAvailMegabytes

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Data read from disk in megabytes. Metrics are aggregated in one minute intervals.

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of total nodes. This total includes some of Active Nodes, Idle Nodes, Unusable Nodes, Premepted Nodes, Leaving Nodes
metricSpecifications.name: Total Nodes

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of Acitve nodes. These are the nodes which are actively running a job.
metricSpecifications.name: Active Nodes

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of idle nodes. Idle nodes are the nodes which are not running any jobs but can accept new job if available.
metricSpecifications.name: Idle Nodes

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of unusable nodes. Unusable nodes are not functional due to some unresolvable issue. Azure will recycle these nodes.
metricSpecifications.name: Unusable Nodes

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of preempted nodes. These nodes are the low priority nodes which are taken away from the available node pool.
metricSpecifications.name: Preempted Nodes

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of leaving nodes. Leaving nodes are the nodes which just finished processing a job and will go to Idle state.
metricSpecifications.name: Leaving Nodes

metricSpecifications.name: Preempted Cores
